prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D watercolor painting of a humorous scene for a greeting card front. A cartoon-illustrated young East Asian woman and a young Southeast Asian man, highly resembling the people in the reference photo, are standing side-by-side in a comically oversized dim sum steamer basket. The woman, on the left, has long, straight dark brown hair, wears gold-rimmed glasses, and has a bright, happy smile. She is wearing a light blue crewneck sweatshirt (plain, no logo) and black pants. The man, standing slightly behind her on the right, has short, dark, textured hair and a wide, cheerful grin. He is wearing a plain tan-colored hoodie and dark maroon pants. They are both holding giant, comically large chopsticks, struggling playfully to pick up a single, tiny shumai dumpling that sits between them in the steamer. The entire scene is rendered in a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds. In the center of the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Thanks for everything, Lao Lao! You're the best, dim sum and then some!" The background is a simple, light cream color with soft, subtle watercolor washes to keep the focus on the characters.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
